metadata.name: The ghost of Kiyv
metadata.description:
The ghost of Kyiv is a myth or a legend or the truth who knows, but he protects the city.

25% goes to [COME BACK ALIVE](https://www.comebackalive.in.ua/) 
25% goes to [MAGNA](https://www.magna.org/en/)
50% goes to my family and my friends and 
territorial defense
